          "value": "entities-classes",
          "@type": "Annotation"
        }
      ],
      "description": "An Agent is a dpv:Entity that is (a) acting on behalf of another Entity;\nand (b) is authorised to do so by that Entity",
      "comments": [
        "the Entity the Agent is acting on behalf of can be a human or non-human\nand a legal or non-legal entity. For specific distinction, see\ndpv:LegalAgent and tech:MachineAgent. The form and validity of\nauthorisation through which the Agent is empowered to represent and act\non behalf of the Entity is not defined or covered in this concept"
      ],
      "in_subset": [
        "entities_subset"
      ],
