      "annotations": [
        {
          "tag": "skos_in_scheme",
          "value": "entities-legalrole-classes",
          "@type": "Annotation"
        }
      ],
      "description": "A group of Data Controllers that jointly determine the purposes and\nmeans of processing",
      "comments": [
        "While Joint Data Controllers operate together, they are made up of\nindividually distinct legal entities. To indicate the membership of this\ngroup, hasDataController should be used to denote each Data Controller.\nThe concept of Joint Data Controllers also allows specifying a single\ngroup as the 'Controller' and to specify role and responsibilities\nwithin that group for each entity using DPV's concepts (e.g.\nisImplementedByEntity)"
      ],
      "in_subset": [
