          "tag": "skos_in_scheme",
          "value": "organisational-measures-classes",
          "@type": "Annotation"
        }
      ],
      "description": "Policy regarding deletion of data",
      "comments": [
        "Deletion and Erasure are distinct activities where deletion refers to\nlogical removal of data with the possibility of retrieval whereas\nerasure refers to destruction of data such that it cannot be retrieved.\nSee dpv:DataErasurePolicy"
      ],
      "in_subset": [
        "personal_data_subset"
