    {
      "name": "NonPersonalData",
      "definition_uri": "https://w3id.org/lmodel/dpv/NonPersonalData",
      "annotations": [
        {
          "tag": "skos_in_scheme",
          "value": "personal-data-classes",
          "@type": "Annotation"
        }
      ],
      "description": "Data that is not Personal Data",
      "comments": [
        "The term NonPersonalData is provided to distinguish between PersonalData\nand other data, e.g. for indicating which data is regulated by privacy\nlaws. To specify personal data that has been anonymised, the concept\nAnonymisedData should be used as the anonymisation process has a risk of\nnot being fully effective and such anonymous data may be found to be\npersonal data depending on circumstances."
      ],
      "in_subset": [
        "personal_data_subset"
      ],
      "from_schema": "https://w3id.org/lmodel/dpv",
      "aliases": [
        "Non-Personal Data"
      ],
      "mappings": [
        "dpv:NonPersonalData",
        "dpv:NonPersonalData"
      ],
      "exact_mappings": [
        "dpv_upstream:NonPersonalData",
        "dpv_owl:NonPersonalData"
      ],
      "is_a": "DpvData",
      "slots": [
        "id"
      ],
      "slot_usage": {},
      "class_uri": "https://w3id.org/lmodel/dpv/NonPersonalData",
      "@type": "ClassDefinition"
    },
    {
      "name": "Notification",
      "definition_uri": "https://w3id.org/lmodel/dpv/Notification",
      "annotations": [
        {
          "tag": "skos_in_scheme",
          "value": "organisational-measures-classes",
          "@type": "Annotation"
        }
      ],
      "description": "Notification represents the provision of a notice i.e. notifying",
      "comments": [
        "Notice refers to the information whereas Notification refers to the\nprovision of that notice. The distinction is important as there are\nspecific obligations associated with notice and notifications. For\nexample, a data breach notice refers to the information about the breach\nintended to be provided to another entity, whereas notification refers\nto the act of providing the entity with the notice"
      ],
      "in_subset": [
        "personal_data_subset"
      ],
      "from_schema": "https://w3id.org/lmodel/dpv",
      "aliases": [
        "Notification"
      ],
      "mappings": [
        "dpv:Notification",
        "dpv:Notification"
      ],
      "exact_mappings": [
        "dpv_upstream:Notification",
        "dpv_owl:Notification"
      ],
      "is_a": "OrganisationalMeasure",
      "slots": [
        "id"
      ],
      "slot_usage": {},
      "class_uri": "https://w3id.org/lmodel/dpv/Notification",
      "@type": "ClassDefinition"
    },
