      "description": "Purposes associated with verifying or authenticating age or age related\ninformation as a form of security",
      "comments": [
        "Age Verification can include verification of the exact age, e.g. being\n21 years old, a date, e.g. birth date is 01 January 1969, or a\ncondition, e.g. age is over 21 years and the person is an adult.\nSpecific dedicated resources should be used to further express\ninformation and processes associated with Age Verification, for example\nthe Age Verification Vocabulary https://w3id.org/age/"
      ],
      "in_subset": [
        "processing_subset"
      ],
      "from_schema": "https://w3id.org/lmodel/dpv",
