    {
      "name": "AssistiveAutomation",
      "definition_uri": "https://w3id.org/lmodel/dpv/AssistiveAutomation",
      "annotations": [
        {
          "tag": "skos_in_scheme",
          "value": "processing-context-classes",
          "@type": "Annotation"
        }
      ],
      "description": "Level of automation corresponding to Level 1 in ISO/IEC 22989:2022 where\nautomation is limited to parts of the system or a specific part of the\nsystem in a manner that does not change the control of the human in\nusing/driving the system",
      "comments": [
        "Human Involvement is implied here, specifically the ability to make\ndecisions regarding operations, but also possibly for intervention,\noversight, and verification"
      ],
      "in_subset": [
        "processing_subset"
      ],
      "from_schema": "https://w3id.org/lmodel/dpv",
      "aliases": [
        "Assistive Automation"
      ],
      "mappings": [
        "dpv:AssistiveAutomation",
        "dpv:AssistiveAutomation"
      ],
      "exact_mappings": [
        "dpv_upstream:AssistiveAutomation",
        "dpv_owl:AssistiveAutomation"
      ],
      "is_a": "AutomationLevel",
      "slots": [
        "id"
      ],
      "slot_usage": {},
      "class_uri": "https://w3id.org/lmodel/dpv/AssistiveAutomation",
      "@type": "ClassDefinition"
    },
    {
      "name": "AutomatedDecisionMaking",
      "definition_uri": "https://w3id.org/lmodel/dpv/AutomatedDecisionMaking",
      "annotations": [
        {
          "tag": "skos_in_scheme",
          "value": "processing-context-classes",
          "@type": "Annotation"
        }
      ],
      "description": "Processing that involves automated decision making",
      "comments": [
        "Automated decision making can be defined as \u201cthe ability to make\ndecisions by technological means without human involvement.\u201d\n(\u201cGuidelines on Automated individual decision-making and Profiling for\nthe purposes of Regulation 2016/679 (wp251rev.01)\u201d, 2018, p. 8)"
      ],
      "in_subset": [
        "processing_subset"
      ],
      "from_schema": "https://w3id.org/lmodel/dpv",
      "aliases": [
        "Automated Decision Making"
      ],
      "mappings": [
        "dpv:AutomatedDecisionMaking",
        "dpv:AutomatedDecisionMaking"
      ],
      "exact_mappings": [
        "dpv_upstream:AutomatedDecisionMaking",
        "dpv_owl:AutomatedDecisionMaking"
      ],
      "related_mappings": [
        "iso22989:Decision"
      ],
      "is_a": "DecisionMaking",
      "slots": [
        "id"
      ],
      "slot_usage": {},
      "class_uri": "https://w3id.org/lmodel/dpv/AutomatedDecisionMaking",
      "@type": "ClassDefinition"
    },
    {
      "name": "AutomatedScoringOfIndividuals",
      "definition_uri": "https://w3id.org/lmodel/dpv/AutomatedScoringOfIndividuals",
      "annotations": [
        {
          "tag": "skos_in_scheme",
          "value": "processing-context-classes",
          "@type": "Annotation"
        }
      ],
      "description": "Processing that involves automated scoring of individuals",
      "comments": [
        "Scoring can lead to the action being considered Decision Making if the\nscoring is itself a decision - see 2023-MAR-16 opinion of Advocate\nGeneral on Case C 634/21. Therefore, the assessment of whether scoring\nwas automated or not is important given the legal obligations\nsurrounding automated decision making e.g. in GDPR"
      ],
      "in_subset": [
        "processing_subset"
      ],
      "from_schema": "https://w3id.org/lmodel/dpv",
      "aliases": [
        "Automated Scoring of Individuals"
      ],
      "mappings": [
        "dpv:AutomatedScoringOfIndividuals",
        "dpv:AutomatedScoringOfIndividuals"
      ],
      "exact_mappings": [
        "dpv_upstream:AutomatedScoringOfIndividuals",
        "dpv_owl:AutomatedScoringOfIndividuals"
      ],
      "is_a": "ScoringOfIndividuals",
      "slots": [
        "id"
      ],
      "slot_usage": {},
      "class_uri": "https://w3id.org/lmodel/dpv/AutomatedScoringOfIndividuals",
      "@type": "ClassDefinition"
    },
