      ],
      "description": "Human involvement for the purposes of exercising interventions over the\nspecified operations in context",
      "comments": [
        "Intervention indicates the ability to intervene in operations, which can\nbe at various stages. It maps to Conditional and High automation models."
      ],
      "in_subset": [
