          "tag": "skos_in_scheme",
          "value": "processing-context-classes",
          "@type": "Annotation"
        }
      ],
      "description": "Human involvement for the purposes of verification of specified context\nto ensure its operations, inputs, or outputs are correct or are\nacceptable.",
      "comments": [
        "Verification by itself does not imply ability to Control, Intervene, or\nhaving Oversight."
