          "tag": "skos_in_scheme",
          "value": "processing-context-classes",
          "@type": "Annotation"
        }
      ],
      "description": "Level of automation corresponding to Level 2 in ISO/IEC 22989:2022 where\nthe automation is present in multiple parts of the system or in a manner\nthat does not require the human to control/use these parts while still\nretaining control over the system",
      "comments": [
        "Human Involvement is implied here, specifically the ability to Control\noperations, but also possibly for intervention, oversight, and\nverification"
