        "This concept was modified as a breaking change in v2.3 with the\nintroduction of `dpv:ServiceManagement`. This concept should therefore\nbe used only to describe the provision of a service, and should not be\nused to represent its management, monitoring, or other non-provision\nrelated purposes (see the taxonomy for other Service Management related\npurposes)"
      ],
