    {
      "name": "Tracking",
      "definition_uri": "https://w3id.org/lmodel/dpv/Tracking",
      "annotations": [
        {
          "tag": "skos_in_scheme",
          "value": "processing-classes",
          "@type": "Annotation"
        }
      ],
      "description": "to use data to track a specific factor (e.g. a human or their\nactivities) across multiple distinct contexts",
      "comments": [
        "Tracking is a widely used (and abused) concept and therefore carries\nseveral distinct interpretations, for example see Do Not Track which\ndefines tracking in the context of the web, and where other forms of\ntracking such as location tracking or physical biometric tracking may\nexist which are defined differently. For this concept, DPVCG defines\nTracking in the broadest possible sense and strongly recommends adopters\nto provide their specific definition or interpretation by either\nextending this concept, through a usage note, or by contributing the\nspecific term back to DPVCG for inclusion in DPV or an extension. This\nconcept may change in the future based on developments in privacy and\nlegal spaces. In DPV, Tracking is defined as a type of processing\noperation that may collect and/or may use data - which covers both\ninitial collection and usage as well as subsequent use of existing data\nto track an individual. The classification of Tracking as a processing\noperation also implies that it is not sufficient as a Purpose on its own\nand therefore a suitable purpose from the DPV taxonomy should be used to\njustify it."
      ],
      "in_subset": [
        "processing_subset"
      ],
      "from_schema": "https://w3id.org/lmodel/dpv",
      "aliases": [
        "Tracking"
      ],
      "mappings": [
        "dpv:Tracking",
        "dpv:Tracking"
      ],
      "exact_mappings": [
        "dpv_upstream:Tracking",
        "dpv_owl:Tracking"
      ],
      "is_a": "Use",
      "mixins": [
        "Processing"
      ],
      "slots": [
        "id"
      ],
      "slot_usage": {},
      "class_uri": "https://w3id.org/lmodel/dpv/Tracking",
      "@type": "ClassDefinition"
    },
    {
      "name": "TrackingByFirstParty",
      "definition_uri": "https://w3id.org/lmodel/dpv/TrackingByFirstParty",
      "annotations": [
        {
          "tag": "skos_in_scheme",
          "value": "processing-classes",
          "@type": "Annotation"
